      updatesTitle: "Latest updates from the studio",
      updatesCopy:
        "Share fresh drops, commission openings, and in-progress moments without switching to a separate demo layout.",
      catalogKicker: "Available works",
      catalogTitle: "Live pieces and creative offers",
      catalogCopy:
        "Every card below is powered by the active store catalog, so buyers move from discovery to listing view without hitting dead ends.",
      highlightsTitle: "How this art template behaves live",
      highlights: [
        "Real listings stay visual-first without hiding price, delivery, or stock information.",
